If a fallback is not set, null models will cause the error drawable to be displayed. If
   * the error drawable is not set, the placeholder will be displayed.

fallback
error
placeholder
  val requestOptions = RequestOptions.centerCropTransform()
            .error(R.drawable.placeholder_avatar)
            .fallback(R.drawable.placeholder_avatar)

        return requestBuilder.run {
            load(url)
                .apply(requestOptions)
                .submit(width, height)
                .get()
        }


